messages.message: Is there any sort of approval process or procedure for modifying `IBOCRRecordDict`? Would like to add some sort of `online_origin` field that holds information about a record that comes from Fetch Files (i.e. the url it came from, the title of the webpage, maybe the search used to find that record)
I'd work with @shaunak and @Karthik S on this
Sounds good.  Currently Fetch Files step doesn’t produce any IBOCR / IBDOC (I Think).  We’ll have to first figure out how to make this work.
